{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5449014074","title":"关于文学艺术的两个批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f200decbe","index":0,"year":1963,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"fc7caba8ee","index":1,"year":1964,"month":6,"day":27,"articleId":"5449014074"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","name":"红旗一九六七年第九期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a49c3572c7","type":"paragraph","text":"关于文学艺术的两个批示","index":0,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"89028d15e6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"0f7f9705ce","type":"paragraph","text":"一，一九六三年十二月十二日的批示","index":2,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"f442d624bf","type":"paragraph","text":"各种艺术形式-戏剧、曲艺、音乐、美术舞蹈、电影、诗和文学等等，周题不少，人数很多，社会主义改造在许多部门中，至今收效基微。许多部门至今还是“死人”统治着。不能低估电影、新诗、民歌、美术、小说的成绩，但其中的周题也不少。至于戏剧等部门，周题就更大了。社会经济基础已经改变了，为这个基础服务的上层建筑之一的艺术部门，至今还是大周题。这需要从调查研究着手，认真地抓起来。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"6b12cbfb55","type":"paragraph","text":"许多共产党人热心提偶封建主义和资本主义的艺术，却不热心提借社会主义的艺术，艺非叫啦怪事。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"16f66c1a22","type":"paragraph","text":"二，一九六四年六月二十七日的批示","index":5,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"1fa05eeac1","type":"paragraph","text":"这些协会和他们所掌握的刊物的大多数（据说有少数几个好的），十五年来，基本上（不是一切人）","index":6,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"119bfb88e8","type":"paragraph","text":"中不执行党的政策，做官当老常，不去接近工农兵不去反映社会主义的革命和建设。最近儿年，党然","index":7,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"},{"id":"803f0d3227","type":"paragraph","text":"中事跌到了修正主义的边缘。如不认真改造，势必在将来的某一天，要变成像句牙利装多菲俱乐部那样的团体。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074"}],"page":{"id":"6baece91cb","publicationId":"d4e5bc82-4b7e-437b-89ae-e720f47d3d82","articleId":"5449014074","start":10,"end":11}}}},"__N_SSG":true}